OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,6,Flocally heavy, mainly on western hills
OL,7,Fat first. The rain turning light and
OL,8,Fpatchy in the afternoon. Most places
OL,9,Fbecoming largely dry with perhaps some
OL,10,Fbrighter spells by late afternoon.
OL,11,FWindy along the coast. Mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLargely dry with variable
OL,14,Famounts of cloud and occasional clear
OL,15,Fspells, especially in the east.
OL,16,FCloudier in the west, with outbreaks
OL,17,Fof rain on western hills. Breezy. A
OL,18,Fmild night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
