OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA slow-moving band of rain
OL,6,Fwill gradually move eastwards across
OL,7,Fall parts on Monday morning,
OL,8,Ffragmenting as it does so. Becoming
OL,9,Fdry with sunny spells in the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FAfter
OL,13,Fa chilly start, Tuesday will be dry
OL,14,Fwith sunny spells and light winds.
OL,15,FSimilar conditions Wednesday.
OL,16,FRemaining dry with sunny spells
OL,17,FThursday. Temperatures generally a
OL,18,Flittle above the average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
